oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Christian Brothers Centennial: CBHS Souvenir
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Souvenirs; Centennial celebrations
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Christian Brothers High School produced this "money" to be a souvenir of the 100th anniversary of the school. One side depicted the original Adams Street school and the modern CBHS on Walnut Grove; the other, the centennial dates.
